event: message_saved
data: {"messageId":"NzpsT-in3A8s1tH9kk1t6","role":"user","content":"Perform a complete infrastructure health audit of this OpenAgentic platform. I need you to:\n\n1. Run admin_full_system_test to check all backend services\n2. Use admin_system_postgres_health_check to verify database health, then run admin_system_postgres_raw_query to show me the top 10 largest tables by row count\n3. Use admin_system_redis_health_check and admin_system_redis_list_keys_by_pattern with pattern '*' to show cache utilization\n4. Use admin_system_milvus_health_check and admin_system_milvus_list_collections to show vector DB status\n5. Use k8s_cluster_health to get overall cluster status\n6. Use k8s_list_pods in the agentic-dev namespace and report any pods not in Running state\n7. Use prometheus_health_summary to check monitoring stack\n8. Use loki_search_errors to find any errors in the last 1 hour\n\nPresent the results as a structured health report with RED/YELLOW/GREEN status for each subsystem. Include actual metrics (row counts, memory usage, pod counts). Do NOT skip any of these checks.","timestamp":"2026-02-20T21:50:37.314Z","source":"database","confirmed":true}

